{
  "stem": "15694.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two soldiers-- I'm so sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germ-- the, the voices turned out to be German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I withdrew further into the wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I assumed there were soldiers on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Came along-- I didn't know they had a dog with them or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was obviously a patrol.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I could even hear what they said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they didn't see anything important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They only spoke about a comrade who was lucky who broke a leg just before he was going to be sent to the Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as they went past, I went back to the rails.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, will I or will I not?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But to go back and do nothing, it's just not my nature.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one patrol-- will there be more?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to do something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started heaping little stones on the rails and against the sleepers, and at first, a big branch across the rails onto the stones, and on the top of the branch with the big end towards the engine, bigger branches against the sleepers behind two of those, and then more woo-- more little-- tapering the wood, and you know, hoping sort of in my mind I'm-- I wasn't exactly experienced in that sort of work-- and hoping and imaging in my mind that that would lift the engine out of the, out of the rail and hopefully kill the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 100
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, having done it, it was already getting a little bit lighter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I, I run back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was awake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he immediately scolded me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told me that you-- it's a very stupid thing I've done.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
